Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:08.00,N_Pri,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Apprentice Negi Springfield was sent to Japan to teach a class of Mahora Academy’s middle school girls for training.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.25,0:00:11.86,N_Pri,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, however, there is a vampire on the loose within the Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.05,0:00:16.65,N_Pri,,0000,0000,0000,,And, on a moonlit night, a vampire girl appears before Negi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:24.37,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve waited for this day, Negi Springfield, son of the Thousand Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:29.15,N_Pri,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Who is she? What is her motive? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.39,0:02:19.58,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Release Nodoka-san right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.61,0:02:22.98,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I’m done with her anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:33.04,N_Nod,Nodoka,0000,0000,0000,,Negi-sensei…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:38.72,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Well, aren’t you the kind one, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.36,0:02:49.28,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I have a virgin's blood, do you really think you can match my magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:52.18,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,Aniki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:12.83,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,I underestimated you. That much power for a 10-year old…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:15.24,N_Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, no doubt you’re his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:17.28,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Who exactly are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:22.08,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.75,0:03:26.50,N_Kuu,Kuu,0000,0000,0000,,Where was the last time you saw her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:27.81,N_Set,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,At the entrance hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:33.44,N_Kuu,Kuu,0000,0000,0000,,Negi-bouzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:35.96,N_Set,Secchan,0000,0000,0000,,Konoka-ojousama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:37.72,N_Set,Secchan,0000,0000,0000,,Ojousama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:41.45,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh…? Secchan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:42.73,N_Set,Secchan,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:45.47,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,I…don’t know…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:47.19,N_Set,Secchan,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:51.41,N_Set,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s an injury on Ojousama’s neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:53.59,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Nodoka-san! Nodoka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:59.00,N_Set,Secchan,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It disappeared…was it just my imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:01.51,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What is…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:10.21,N_Har,Saotome,0000,0000,0000,,Nodoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:12.63,N_Yue,Yue,0000,0000,0000,,Nodoka! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:19.07,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Nodoka-san…This is great! You’re okay now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:28.33,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Eh…? I never noticed it because of her hair, but…she’s got a really cute face…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:33.36,N_Nod,Nodoka,0000,0000,0000,,Ne-Negi-sensei’s face is so close... W-what do I do…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:36.98,N_2,Yue and Saotome,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm now…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:51.27,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that scared the crap out of me. But Aniki, isn’t it great that they didn’t see your magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:53.40,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess you’re right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:56.85,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Asuna-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:00.35,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,But I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.87,0:05:03.13,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Mage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:05.78,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,Are you freaking serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:07.66,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Uwah! The rat can talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:10.08,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,Dumbass! I’m not a rat! I’m an ermine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:15.13,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Mmhmm; you made this rat talk because of your magic, didn’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:17.92,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,Hell no! I’ve been like this the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:22.55,N_Kam,,0000,0000,0000,,And I’m not a rat, I’m an ermine! An ermine! Remember that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:24.26,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,You’re noisy as heck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:25.57,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:28.72,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:35.13,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you saw me use magic isn’t something I can let slide. Asuna-san, I have to erase your memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.38,0:05:36.44,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,My memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:03.67,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Finished! Okay, now, Asuna-san, exactly {\i1}what{\i0} am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.15,0:06:05.01,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,A mage, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:06.32,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,CORRECT!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:07.90,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.90,0:06:09.48,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,Didn’t go away, Aniki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.51,0:06:15.77,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.53,0:06:19.54,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,What in the heck are you doing, Aniki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:24.93,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you trying to do, you brat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:26.94,N_2,Asuna and Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.89,0:06:28.95,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,This ain’t gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:29.91,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:37.88,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,So you finished your classes as a mage...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:38.61,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:45.65,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,If he’s able to complete his training and find a partner as well, Aniki’ll be able to rank up as a mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:47.76,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,A partner, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.12,0:06:55.76,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. If I’m aiming to reach the highest level of mages, Magister Magi, I have to find an appropriate partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:07:02.80,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,Aniki isn’t an adult yet, so he can’t make an official contract with a partner; he can only issue provisional contracts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:05.02,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Provisional contract?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:10.81,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange, he is able to give pretty much {\i1}anyone{\i0} a provisional contract under an alias and can exchange them as he pleases.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:14.97,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,So in other words, you’re still a mage apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:20.33,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,I graduated from the Magic Academy! I’m not an apprentice anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:27.53,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,An appropriate partner, eh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:39.62,N_Set,Secchan,0000,0000,0000,,Konoka-ojousama, I promise I won’t let events like the one from tonight repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.61,0:07:45.06,N_Set,Secchan,0000,0000,0000,,We have been protecting the Konoe house for generations...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:49.73,N_Set,,0000,0000,0000,,and I, Setsuna, with pride for the Sakurazaki family, will protect her, even at the cost of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:57.28,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,Whaddya think, Ane-san? Wanna make a provisional contract?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.48,0:07:58.56,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Chamo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:00.90,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,How do you make one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:03.22,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Uh…um…well…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.02,0:08:07.54,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,What are you getting all hot n’ bothered about, Aniki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.64,0:08:10.30,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,I-I’m not hot and bothered or anything…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:12.22,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:14.78,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta KISS, Ane-san! Kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:20.87,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,For mages, exchanging a kiss will enable the partner to bind to the provisional contract!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:22.43,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,Easy, isn’t it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:30.60,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…really? I-is {\i1}that{\i0} what it is? That’s pretty easy-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:38.99,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,B-but it’s not like I’ll want to be your partner, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:44.96,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-yes, I know! A mage and his partner must be together, and if they have no confidence, then it’s no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:46.22,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Then it’s impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.22,0:08:47.33,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, VERY impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:51.81,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, oi, you guys are acting like kids, geez! Learn to get along!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:54.82,N_Kam,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are gonna be under the same roof living together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:56.43,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?! Together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:58.14,N_Kam,Chamo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, ya see…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:09:01.46,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT THE HELL IS THAT!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:19.05,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Negi…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.18,0:09:26.32,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,When did you get in? Is it even okay for a teacher to enter a student’s room without permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.89,0:09:31.64,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good, Eva. Countless full moons and you’re doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:34.06,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,I’m a vampire, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:39.99,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,I erased the wounds after you bit the girls; they’re not going to become your servants.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:41.45,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,It’s good to prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:47.84,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,It’s my job. Don’t do it again, okay? You’ll receive a heavier punishment otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.29,0:09:49.76,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not afraid of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:51.31,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,Evangeline.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:53.35,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve waited 15 years for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:24.92,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,EAT THIS!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:52.35,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,That imbecile casted a spell on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:58.59,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,This is the result of it all. I have to be the one locked up in an Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:01.99,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,This is your punishment, though. Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,0:11:06.46,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,But if I…was able to take the blood of the son of the Thousand Master, I-!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:09.53,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t even think about it, Eva. I understand how you feel, but don’t resort to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:14.71,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,What in the hell do you know?! Growing up to be a normal man…living freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.14,0:11:19.60,N_Eva,,0000,0000,0000,,How in the hell can you understand the pain and suffering I feel from having to live an eternal hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:20.75,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,Eva…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.84,0:11:27.64,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:40.92,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta deliver papers…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:50.08,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell are you sleeping here?! You’re supposed to be on the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:53.10,N_Asu,,0000,0000,0000,,Aigh, I shouldn’t have let him here in the first pla-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.40,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:12:02.90,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,You’re such a kid. When you wake up, you’re in for it big time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.09,0:12:12.20,N_Kae,Kaede,0000,0000,0000,,So all together, this makes three people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.51,0:12:14.22,N_Mak,Makie,0000,0000,0000,,See? I told you it was real!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:18.70,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,I guess, but unlike you, we didn’t get anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:23.40,N_Mak,Makie,0000,0000,0000,,But about that…last night, it disappeared! See?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.88,0:12:29.86,N_Aya,Ayaka,0000,0000,0000,,I told you the blood sucking ordeal was a farce. All three of you just happened to see the same dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.36,0:12:31.15,N_Mak,Makie,0000,0000,0000,,Pres!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:33.81,N_Yue,Yue,0000,0000,0000,,Did it happen to look like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.71,0:12:39.38,N_FF,Fuka,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it? Is that the chupacabra?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:43.04,N_Kon,Konoka,0000,0000,0000,,Well…we were together, but I didn’t see that creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:45.63,N_Nod,Nodoka,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t think that’s it…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.94,0:12:47.57,N_Mak,Makie,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! It was Dracula!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:50.08,N_2,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Dracula!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:53.41,N_Har,Saotome,0000,0000,0000,,I see…so there was a Dracula in there…eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:13:00.88,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm…It wasn’t just a chupacabra; Dracula was in there, too…this’ll be interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:06.66,N_Yue,Yue,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it’s Chupacabra vs Dracula; it’s gonna be the Academy’s greatest epic battle in that aspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:07.60,N_2,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Battle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:10.18,N_Mak,,0000,0000,0000,,But like, what's with you guys and chupacabras?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:11.77,N_Aya,Ayaka,0000,0000,0000,,Idiots, all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:14.38,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Homeroom will now begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:17.76,N_Aya,Ayaka,0000,0000,0000,,Rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:19.66,N_Aya,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:23.76,N_Aya,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened, Negi-sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:25.75,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing, I just…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.68,0:13:36.97,N_Aya,Ayaka,0000,0000,0000,,What happened? Did someone hit you? Who was it? Who was the banshee that did it?! As class president, I cannot allow this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:39.08,N_Chi,Chisame,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck does being president have to do with it…?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:42.86,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be fine, Iinchou-san; I just fell down, that’s all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:49.59,N_Aya,Ayaka,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn’t look like a bump from falling. But Negi-sensei, if I were to protect you from that banshee…!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:52.71,N_Aya,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, kind me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:56.64,N_Chi,Chisame,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, you piss me off, you Shotacon woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:14:00.78,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let me take attendance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:05.01,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Those two are absent again…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.94,0:14:10.57,N_Yuu,Yuna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Eva and Chachamaru? They’re never here, so don’t worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:12.22,N_Kuu,Kuu Fei,0000,0000,0000,,They ditch class, aru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:13.99,N_Yue,Yue,0000,0000,0000,,Is it senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.34,0:14:16.46,N_Hak,Satomi,0000,0000,0000,,If that’s the case, it’s sabotage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.93,0:14:20.13,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you say sabotage is okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:42.61,N_Nat,Natsumi,0000,0000,0000,,What’s that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.63,0:14:48.75,N_Any,Anya,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it feels great out here…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:53.78,N_Any,Anya,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, thank you, Nekane-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.98,0:14:58.50,N_Any,Anya,0000,0000,0000,,It’s too bad that I have to say goodbye to all this scenery…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:03.79,N_Nek,Nekane,0000,0000,0000,,London is a very nice place, Anya. It’s most suitable for your studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.64,0:15:06.73,N_Any,Anya,0000,0000,0000,,You said the same thing to Negi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:08.96,N_Nek,Nekane,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my…did I now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.69,0:15:14.20,N_Any,Anya,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Negi’s doing well…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.96,0:15:18.47,N_Nek,Nekane,0000,0000,0000,,He’ll be fine…I’m sure he’s fine…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.21,0:15:23.93,N_Nek,,0000,0000,0000,,Negi…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.66,0:15:30.97,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,The day is finally over! I did a bunch of studying today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:33.87,N_Aya,Ayaka,0000,0000,0000,,More like a bunch of sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:35.93,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, pretty much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:36.99,N_Aya,Ayaka,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness gracious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:39.27,N_FF,Fuka,0000,0000,0000,,Asuna! Let’s play badminton!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.51,0:15:42.14,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds great! Count me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:50.29,N_Hak,Satomi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:57.56,N_Hak,Satomi,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn’t you bring this up with me last night, Eva-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.86,0:16:01.09,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry. I didn’t think it was going to be this bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:03.97,N_Cha,Chachamaru,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be okay, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:09.28,N_Hak,Satomi,0000,0000,0000,,Not with those wounds! Goodness, what made it so bad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:13.70,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Eva-san, Chachamaru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.67,0:16:20.85,N_Neg,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleasure to meet you. I’ll be the new homeroom teacher for the A class. Did…did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:22.60,N_Hak,Satomi,0000,0000,0000,,Chachamaru’s going through a break down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.24,0:16:24.02,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,…break down?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.02,0:16:26.44,N_Hak,Satomi,0000,0000,0000,,Can’t you tell? She’s broken! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:29.10,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,…a machine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:35.49,N_Hak,Satomi,0000,0000,0000,,Why the shock, Negi-sensei? I made Chachamaru. Didn’t you hear about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:39.69,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Chachamaru is a robot?! I thought she was a student this whole time…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:40.99,N_Cha,Chachamaru,0000,0000,0000,,I’m a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:45.19,N_Cha,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a robot, but I am also an 8th grader.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:47.10,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,I…I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:48.67,N_Cha,Chachamaru,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.06,0:16:51.48,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! It’s not a bad thing at all…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:55.53,N_Cha,Chachamaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear. Looks like something bad happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:58.02,N_Hak,Satomi,0000,0000,0000,,We have to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:04.97,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,A robot student…living in the Academy…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.61,0:17:06.98,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Wait a minute…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:13.69,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that…? If that’s the case, then the vampire is…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.48,0:17:17.79,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,You’re correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:19.65,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Takamichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:26.07,N_Cha,Chachamaru,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry if I’ve caused any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:27.05,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:33.59,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,Evangeline is a vampire. When she was 10 years old, she laid her eyes on a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.79,0:17:39.04,N_Tak,,0000,0000,0000,,She was bitten and had her blood sucked. Once that happened, a curse was put upon her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:40.12,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,A curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:44.75,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,She would be forever cursed to live a life in the body of a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.86,0:17:50.84,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Perpetual youth? So, you mean to tell me that the figure from last night was…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.35,0:17:57.25,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,On every night with a full moon, Eva can use her power to transform herself into a woman of her dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:18:03.11,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Takamichi…you were the one that cured the wounds of Nodoka-san and the others, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:08.05,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn’t matter what her reasoning is; I can’t forgive her if she harms people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:11.01,N_Tak,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:15.13,N_Hak,Satomi,0000,0000,0000,,Eva-san, fetch me that item there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:17.40,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Heck no. Do it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:19.86,N_Hak,Satomi,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t let go of the hand. Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.19,0:18:21.48,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,I told you ain’t doin’ it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:26.95,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,This thing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.12,0:18:33.19,N_Hak,Satomi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please discard the insulation tape before using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.19,0:18:34.20,N_Hak,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll get an electric shock otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.06,0:18:38.87,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Should’ve said it first, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:42.02,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,She can’t leave the school grounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:46.43,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely. The Thousand Master had made it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.04,0:18:51.07,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Dad did…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.75,0:18:56.43,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,As a vampire, Eva imposed a lot of faults. This is to make up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:06.04,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,She’ll be with her classmates through middle school. But once they graduate, she reverts back to the 7th grade. She just relapses.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:12.25,N_Tak,,0000,0000,0000,,Every... Single... Time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:23.92,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,I understand why Eva causes mischief with Chachamaru. Like Eva, Chachamaru will be a figure that never grows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.69,0:19:29.13,N_Hak,Satomi,0000,0000,0000,,Repairing complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:30.74,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. Really now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:36.15,N_Hak,Satomi,0000,0000,0000,,Try not to touch her so much. She’s a robot, meaning she’s very delicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:48.70,N_Eva,Eva,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I’m glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:51.74,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Is Eva-san after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.77,0:19:55.59,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,Eva is after your blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.04,0:19:57.02,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,My blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:20:06.61,N_Tak,Takahata,0000,0000,0000,,If she gets her hands on the blood of a relative of the Thousand Master, the spell will be eradicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:13.97,N_Tak,,0000,0000,0000,,She’ll be able to flee from this place. She can live in the free world. If that were to happen…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:18.82,N_Tak,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't afford to let her free.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.43,0:20:20.51,N_Neg,Negi,0000,0000,0000,,Takamichi…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.65,0:20:44.33,N_Pri,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight…the target of the vampire girl is only one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:49.54,N_Pri,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate starts to deceive; it's a grieving fate indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:21:01.69,N_Pri,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,What's on your mind, Negi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:12.49,N_Pri,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen next?! You’ll have to wait until next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.33,0:22:51.85,N_Yue,Yue,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy’s running away and carrying something with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.99,0:22:53.61,N_Kae,Kaede,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's go, de gozaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.58,0:22:56.47,N_2,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Baka Rangers!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.12,0:22:58.28,N_Mak,Makie,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.09,0:23:01.68,N_Mak,Makie,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t even get to finish my announcement!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.10,0:23:03.84,N_Kuu,Kuu Fei,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Is that all, aru?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.01,0:23:06.43,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn’t matter, does it? We’re in a hurry, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.43,0:23:10.66,N_Mak,Makie,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t get to go yet, it’s not fair! I didn’t get to finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:13.14,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Aigh, fine, fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.37,0:23:15.23,N_Yue,Yue,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, let’s give it another go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.51,0:23:17.24,N_Mak,Makie,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.31,0:23:22.40,N_2,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,The Mahora Sentai Baka Rangers have arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.43,0:23:25.34,N_Asu,Asuna,0000,0000,0000,,Always having fun! Baka Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:27.58,N_Yue,Yue,0000,0000,0000,,Preference for negatives! Baka Black!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.08,0:23:29.83,N_Kae,Kaede,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I get a dog! Baka Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.32,0:23:32.33,N_Kuu,Kuu Fei,0000,0000,0000,,On the side of the mold! It's... Baka Yellow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.49,0:23:33.66,N_Mak,Makie,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone gets along! Baka Pi-
